            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Deanae </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> aram et <expan><abbr>sig</abbr><ex>illum</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Marius Vic<lb break="no" n="3"/>torinus |(centurio) <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>I <expan><abbr>Ital</abbr><ex>icae</ex></expan> ex voto </ab></div><div n="3" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> posuit </ab></div><div n="4" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Dedicatum </ab></div><div n="5" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> XV <expan><abbr>Kal</abbr><ex>endas</ex></expan> Iuni<lb break="no" n="2"/>as <del rend="erasure">Plautiano II</del> <lb n="3"/><del rend="erasure">et <expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>ublio</ex></expan> Septimio</del> <lb n="4"/><del rend="erasure">Geta II</del> co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Die Inschriften auf der altarförmigen Basis erstrecken sich auf die Vorder- und Rückseite. (B): Božilova, AE 1987: Z. 5 (Rückseite): co(n)s(ulibus).</p>
            </div>
